Harvey Adams https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harvey_Adams 0 Harvey Adams (1889, Warrington, England - 1960, Australia) was an English actor and director who worked extensively in film, stage and radio.He moved to Australia in 1924 for work after a long career, and wound up staying in the country for most of the rest of his life.
